alue of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},{"type":"text","text":" objects. When the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":". Keep this property set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" if","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the view’s legibility is important.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingd